-- LG Display sees TV panel shortage until end-June
-- 
-- Thu Apr 16, 2009 4:00am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/16/us-lgdisplay-shortage-sb-idUSTRE53F1HH20090416

 

 SEOUL  (Reuters) - South Korean flat-screen maker LG Display Co Ltd ( 034220.KS ) ( LPL.N ) said on Thursday it expected the current shortage in television panels to continue until the end of June. 

 An executive at the LCD maker told an earnings conference that the outlook for TV panel supply in the third quarter was still uncertain but that the company was cautiously optimistic. (Reporting by Rhee So-eui, editing by Jonathan Hopfner)